member.example:
This sample shows how to call DeleteAsync with required parameters.

var credential = new DefaultAzureCredential();
var client = new APICollectionOffboardingClient("<subscriptionId>", credential);

Response response = await client.DeleteAsync("<resourceGroupName>", "<serviceName>", "<apiCollectionId>");
Console.WriteLine(response.Status);

This sample shows how to call Delete with required parameters.

var credential = new DefaultAzureCredential();
var client = new APICollectionOffboardingClient("<subscriptionId>", credential);

Response response = client.Delete("<resourceGroupName>", "<serviceName>", "<apiCollectionId>");
Console.WriteLine(response.Status);
